data.description: Welcome to Lee's Crossing! This charming 2 bedrooms, 2 baths Corner lot villa offers comfort and style. The upgraded kitchen boasts stainless steel and black appliances, white cabinets and granite countertops. The open floorplan, with a vaulted ceiling, creates a spacious atmosphere, perfect for entertaining. Built-in features enhance functionality. Enjoy privacy in the fenced-in patio, ideal for outdoor gatherings. Your villa includes a private driveway for convenience and exclusivity. 2022 ROOF, EXTERIOR AND INTERIOR FRESH PAINT. Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, I-95, Turnpike and schools. Don't miss the unique opportunity to call this place ''HOME'''!
